usdIpProfileAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the IP Profile Manager component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdIpProfileAgentV1.name: usdIpProfileAgentV1
usdIpProfileAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the IP Profile component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the IP Profile Manager component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 1.x system releases.
usdIpProfileAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the profile loopback object changed.

usdIpProfileAgentV2.name: usdIpProfileAgentV2
usdIpProfileAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the IP Profile component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the IP Profile Manager component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 2.x system releases.
usdIpProfileAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when rsIpProfileRowStatus was deprecate and the rsIpProfileSetMap and rsIpProfileSrcAddrValidEnable objects were added.

usdIpProfileAgentV3.name: usdIpProfileAgentV3
usdIpProfileAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the IP Profile component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the IP Profile Manager component is
        supported in the Unisphere RX 3.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdIpProfileAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
